Durban - A BMW caught alight on Old North Coast Road, north of Durban, on Monday evening. Kyle van Reenen of Marshall Security said Marshall Security responded to the scene of the incident and a BMW was engulfed by flames. “The cause of the fire is unknown,” Van Reenen said. “The driver was lucky to escape unharmed.”  To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
